Havoc: a relational programming language.

See the files in doc/ for conceptual background. The reference implementation
provides a REPL based on node.js. For example:

  $ ./ref-repl
  havoc :: ! 'foo = 'bar
  ('foo = 'bar)
  havoc :: 'foo
  'bar
  havoc :: ! ('f x) = ('g = x)
  (('f x) = ('g = x))
  havoc :: ! 'f 10
  ('f 10)
  havoc :: 'g
  10
  havoc :: ^D
  $
